modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/code.view.x:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.code"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
		id="page"
		showNavButton="true"
		navButtonPress="onNavBack"
		title="{/title}"
		icon="img/144_iPad_Retina_Web_Clip.png" >
		<headerContent>
			<Button
				class="sapUiHideOnPhone"
				text="Download"
				icon="sap-icon://download"
				press="onDownload" />
			<Button
				class="sapUiVisibleOnlyOnPhone"
				icon="sap-icon://download"
				press="onDownload" />
		</headerContent>
		<content>
			<IconTabBar
				class="iconTabBarPaddingTop"
				expandable="false"
				selectedKey="{/selectedTab}"
				items="{/files}" >
				<items>
					<IconTabFilter
						key="{name}"
						text="{name}" >
						<content>
							<core:HTML content="{code}" />
						</content>
					</IconTabFilter>
				</items>
			</IconTabBar>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/master.view:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.master"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
		id="page" >
		<customHeader>
			<Toolbar>
				<Button icon="sap-icon://drop-down-list" press="onOpenViewSettings" />
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<Label text="Entities ({entity>/entityCount})" />
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<ToggleButton
						id="compactModeButton"
						text="Compact"
						press="onToggleCompactMode" />
			</Toolbar>
		</customHeader>
		<subHeader>
			<Bar
				id="searchBar">
				<contentMiddle>
					<SearchField
						id="searchField"
						placeholder="Search"
						liveChange="onSearch"
						width="100%" >
					</SearchField>
				</contentMiddle>
			</Bar>
		</subHeader>
		<content>
			<List
				id="list"
				class="myList"
				noDataText="{i18n>masterListNoData}"
				mode="{device>/listMode}"
				selectionChange="onNavToEntity"
				items="{
					path: 'entity>/entities',
					groupHeaderFactory: '.getGroupHeader'
				}" >
				<infoToolbar>
					<Toolbar
						id="vsFilterBar"
						active="true"
						visible="false"
						press="onOpenViewSettings">
						<Label id="vsFilterLabel" />
					</Toolbar>
				</infoToolbar>
				<items>
					<StandardListItem
						title="{entity>name}"
						counter="{entity>sampleCount}"
						type="{device>/listItemType}"
						press="onNavToEntity" />
				</items>
			</List>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/notFound.vi:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.notFound"

	xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
		title="Not Found"
		showNavButton="{device>/isPhone}"
		navButtonPress="onNavBack"
		enableScrolling="false"
		class="titlesSpace" >

			<core:HTML
				id="msgHtml"
				sanitizeContent="true" />
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>

modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/viewSetting:
<core:FragmentDefinition
	xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">
	<ViewSettingsDialog
		confirm="onConfirmViewSettings">
		<groupItems>
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemName}" key="name" selected="true" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemAppComponent}" key="appComponent" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemCategory}" key="category" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemFormFactors}" key="formFactors" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemNamespace}" key="namespace" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemSince}" key="since" />
		</groupItems>
		<filterItems>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemAppComponent}"
				key="appComponent"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/appComponent',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemCategory}"
				key="category"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/category',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemFormFactors}"
				key="formFactors"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/formFactors',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemNamespace}"
				key="namespace"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/namespace',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemSince}"
				key="since"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/since',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
		</filterItems>
	</ViewSettingsDialog>
</core:FragmentDefinition>
